.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, iris, balloon-flower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Flower         | iris | daffodil | bellflower | balloon-flower |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

