.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, january, april
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Birthday   | august  | april | may | january |

