.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, march, december
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the police-officer and the person who's birthday is in march##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Birthday   | march        | december     | july       | june   |

