2. the fan of ambient is between the fan of hip-hop and the architect##2
3. the teacher is in an even position##4
4. the coach is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
5. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the paramedic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient  | jazz  | salsa   |
| Job           | coach  | teacher | architect | paramedic |

