.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, go, domino
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person playing go##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Game         | go  | domino | mah-jongg | bridge |

