.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, november, march
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
6. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in january and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | january   | november  | october      | march       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

