2. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
3. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the police-officer is on the left of the dancer##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Job   | lawyer | chef  | police-officer | dancer        |

