.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, software-developer, accountant, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the musician is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the musician is between the doctor and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Job        | software-developer     | doctor | musician | accountant |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 